wiki.content: On the closing track of SAVAGE MODE II and over a smooth 80s-like beat, “Said N Done” features a 21 Savage rapping about his long span of his lifestyle; going from the cheating of his girl, betrayals and poverty to having a life full of success and pride for the people around Savage, being that he has finally “done” what he “said” earlier in his life. Metro Boomin samples Stephanie Mills‘ 1987 song, “Touch Me Now,” giving a soft ambience accompanied by the typical trap kicks—and beat overall—that Metro usually uses in his work.
